The actor, who is fiercely protective of his personal life married his long term girlfriend, Keletso Molefe on Saturday night at Fleurhof Estate Hills.Leroy and Keletso were together for 13 years before getting hitched.The wedding was attended by Leroy's industry friends including Thomas Gumede and Matli Mohapeloa."Last night at my brother Leroy's wedding. It was a beautiful celebration of love from two of the most loving people!! It was an honour," said Thomas.A post shared by Thomas Gumede (@thomasgumede) on Mar 5, 2017 at 1:25am PSTA post shared by Thomas Gumede (@thomasgumede) on Mar 5, 2017 at 1:24am PST 